data.description: Open floor plan offering over 1320 sq ft with 3 bedrooms, 2.5 baths and finished lower level. Updates included are beautiful wood floors throughout vaulted great room, hall, kitchen and breakfast room. The kitchen offers upgraded staggered cabinets, plus a breakfast bar and overlooks the light filled breakfast room. The Master bedroom suite has a full bath with walk-in shower and is a welcome retreat! Completing the main floor are 2 additional nice size bedrooms and full bath. Lower-level finish has a 22-foot family room for entertaining family and friends & has a walkout to your large backyard. This home is located in Triple "A" Rated Ft. Zumwalt Schools and is close to highways, shopping & parks. This home offers a quick occupancy!! Seller prefers present condition.
